This is how to is_nested of string:
   Remember that depth is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this string's length times:
      Remember that ch is item i in string
      When ch is 91, then:
         Increase depth
      But, if not:
         When ch is 93, then:
            Remember that depth is diff of depth and 1
            When depth is less than 0, then:
               The answer is 0
            End when
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   When depth is 0, then:
